_:N71b8c8767fb6446c889705c697e8da6b <http://schema.org/description> "The Labour Market Evidence Group is made up of the Industrial Strategy Advisory Council, Migration Advisory Committee, Department for Work and Pensions, and Skills England. It is currently chaired by the Migration Advisory Committee. LMEG is an ad-hoc advisory group of the Home Office ." .
